    16	  request-processing entry point because it already owns idempotency and atomic
    17	  result-manifest writes.
    18	- Preserve the existing callback mode so current idempotency tests and callers
    19	  remain compatible.
    20	- Add an explicit dispatch mode: callers provide a `RendererMatrix` and
    21	  `RendererRegistry`; the entry point reads
    22	  `requests/<request_id>.json`, parses JSON into a mapping, invokes
    23	  `dispatch_request(request, matrix, registry)`, and writes the returned
    24	  manifest atomically to `deliverables/<request_id>.result.json`.
    25	- Add a focused integration test that creates two real request files, one
